From BEN WOLFE Subject Re Hardware that Fits mail order In article Christopher Bruce Kidwell I ordered an external floppy drive from them years When I placed the order they said it was in stock and would ship the next A week passed and no I called them up and they said they were out of stock and my drive should ship in weeks or Since I needed the drive right away both my internal hard drive and floppy were dead I cancelled my order and haven't dealt with them Chris Kidwell I too had a very unpleasant experience with Hardware That's Shi It featured repeated lies about when things had shipped a salesperson who was totally ignorant about what he was selling a charge for duties I had specifically been assured were not payable and then a monitor their house brand page monochrome that was the most unadulterated piece of junk it has ever been my misfortune to experience in the world of I shipped it back and they refunded my money but it still cost me something over for long distance charges non refundable taxes and duties and lost Don't deal with